The &lt;a href="2009%20SAFF%20Championship"&gt;2009 SAFF Championship&lt;/a&gt; was an international &lt;a href="Association%20football"&gt;football&lt;/a&gt; tournament held in Bangladesh from 3 to 14 June 2009. The 8 national teams involved in the tournament were required to register a squad of 20 players. The position listed for each player is per the squad list in the official match reports by the SAFF.
